- legal_services includes provider, package, detailed cost breakdown, and total cost; 
- moving_services specifies provider, package, services list, and estimated cost; 
- setup_services covers utility providers, costs (setup and ongoing), and totals; 
- total_budget provides full cost breakdown including ongoing monthly costs. All required details are covered and clearly specified.

